data.description: Beautifully updated home in desirable Selwyn Park! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch with a full unfinished basement sits on a quiet street with a large level front yard and fenced in back yard surrounded by trees for privacy.  Updates throughout the home include new paint throughout, granite kitchen countertops, new hardware on cabinetry, all new stainless steel appliances with gas range, new light fixtures, new luxury vinyl plank flooring in the living room and halls and new carpet in all bedrooms and second living area, freshly painted siding, door and shutters and brand new roof.  The second living area is separated from the kitchen with beautiful french doors and could be used for an office, playroom or entertainment area.  The basement is unfinished, leaving the possibilities endless.  Separate entry to the basement to the fenced back yard. Located just minutes from Southend, South Park and Myers Park with quick access to amazing restaurants, shopping, parks and entertainment.
